column5: Who in the durham area sells drain plugs?  Canadian does not list on website nor does wallmart....
What type of boat?,plugs are different for different boats.
I bought one at ctc not that long ago
Canadian Tire sells boat plugs. Any marine will also have one. Bring you old one with you if you have it or measure the I.D.
I know my Canadian tire has them. I would think yours should to, maybe call if it is a bit of a trip.
Thanks all, called local CT and they have some in store.
I buy 3 at a time just in case;)
